01:53:03,906 --> 01:53:05,073
Hey! Don't run that way!

1088
01:53:46,490 --> 01:53:47,907
Go save the Emperor

1089
01:53:48,157 --> 01:53:50,572
Your Majesty!?

1090
01:53:50,823 --> 01:53:52,322
Let's go over there.

1091
01:54:04,781 --> 01:54:08,530
Your Majesty!

1092
01:54:10,905 --> 01:54:14,614
It's Detective Dee who saved me...

1093
01:54:16,363 --> 01:54:19,073
A rebel army is gathered 30 miles from here.

1094
01:54:19,322 --> 01:54:22,655
They will invade once the Buddha collapses.

1095
01:54:25,280 --> 01:54:28,947
Where's General Yao?

1096
01:54:29,238 --> 01:54:30,446
Yau is here!

1097
01:54:30,781 --> 01:54:33,114
Report the situation outside the city!

1098
01:54:33,406 --> 01:54:35,363
60,000 imperial guards

1099
01:54:35,656 --> 01:54:37,613
were in ambush in Bianzhou before daybreak!

1100
01:54:37,906 --> 01:54:42,320
Call General Zhang to lead 100,000 soldiers

1101
01:54:42,571 --> 01:54:45,238
to attack the enemies in the east

1102
01:54:45,529 --> 01:54:47,363
until the rebels are totally demolished.

1103
01:54:47,614 --> 01:54:48,780
Yes, Your Majesty.

1104
01:54:55,406 --> 01:54:58,113
You were well prepared indeed.

1105
01:54:59,405 --> 01:55:02,447
Detective Dee,

1106
01:55:02,780 --> 01:55:06,781
from this day onwards,

1107
01:55:07,156 --> 01:55:09,821
the whole world shall know you're my savior.

1108
01:55:12,779 --> 01:55:13,989
May I venture to say a few words to you

1109
01:55:15,487 --> 01:55:18,113
in front of the mace?

1110
01:55:18,321 --> 01:55:20,280
Preposterous!

1111
01:55:20,571 --> 01:55:21,905
Stand down.

1112
01:55:22,156 --> 01:55:24,779
Your Majesty!

1113
01:55:25,029 --> 01:55:26,154
I asked you to stand down!

1114
01:55:26,613 --> 01:55:27,988
Stand down, everybody!

1115
01:55:33,779 --> 01:55:36,987
Under Heaven, with this mace as the witness,

1116
01:55:37,321 --> 01:55:43,238
would the sacred Empress Wu please listen:

1117
01:55:46,737 --> 01:55:48,737
On the pretense of magic,

1118
01:55:49,112 --> 01:55:50,571
you wantonly killed clansmen and officials.

1119
01:55:50,945 --> 01:55:52,363
This is unpardonable!

1120
01:55:52,779 --> 01:55:55,363
But society is on the brink of extinction,

1121
01:55:55,696 --> 01:55:57,196
So your punishment is hereby suspended.

1122
01:55:57,571 --> 01:56:00,155
Ruling requires power and stratagems,

1123
01:56:00,446 --> 01:56:03,070
but right and wrong cannot be confused!

1124
01:56:03,403 --> 01:56:05,529
May the Emperor know her every move,

1125
01:56:05,863 --> 01:56:08,571
and let Tang clansmen succeed her,

1126
01:56:08,946 --> 01:56:10,572
so that everything will be back to track.

1127
01:56:14,821 --> 01:56:16,404
You called me ''Emperor''?

1128
01:56:16,737 --> 01:56:21,445
Long live the Emperor! Long Live!

1129
01:56:30,238 --> 01:56:33,945
Officials are lazy nobody can help me.

1130
01:56:34,237 --> 01:56:39,029
For the people, you stay and help me.

1131
01:56:39,405 --> 01:56:42,447
I've been in rebellion several times.

1132
01:56:42,739 --> 01:56:46,904
How dare I meddle with state affairs?

1133
01:56:49,779 --> 01:56:52,988
My assignment is over.

1134
01:56:53,321 --> 01:56:56,904
I'm returning this mace to the late Emperor.

1135
01:57:37,070 --> 01:57:39,113
The truth has come to light...

1136
01:57:39,446 --> 01:57:42,778
The world is at peace finally...

1137
01:57:43,112 --> 01:57:47,030
But Detective Dee is in Phantom Bazaar.

1138
01:57:48,696 --> 01:57:52,320
Whether your fire turtle poison is curable

1139
01:57:52,695 --> 01:57:54,779
will depend on the will of Heaven.

1140
01:57:55,070 --> 01:57:57,154
The will of Heaven is bright and clear,

1141
01:57:57,487 --> 01:57:58,321
but I'm travelling alone.

1142
01:57:58,696 --> 01:58:00,030
Heaven and Earth have no space for me,

1143
01:58:00,404 --> 01:58:02,070
but my heart is at peace.

1144
01:58:06,195 --> 01:58:09,613
The sun is up. Let's go down.

1145
01:58:37,778 --> 01:58:38,404
In 690 A.D.,

1146
01:58:38,612 --> 01:58:39,153
Empress Wu became the first and only

1147
01:58:39,362 --> 01:58:40,278
female emperor in the history of China.

1148
01:58:43,238 --> 01:58:46,195
15 years later, in 705 A.D.,

1149
01:58:46,486 --> 01:58:48,486
Empress Wu retired from the throne,

1150
01:58:48,861 --> 01:58:50,695
returning the title to the Crown Prince,

1151
01:58:51,070 --> 01:58:54,654
in honor of her promise to Detective Dee.

